{"tid":1708255,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【1111三罷｜沙田】喬裝警新城市拘五示威者 速龍唔認得自己友打爆缸","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:56:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T05:31:45.000Z","uid":33775,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bcadf1e9fbbbf2aa811fbf3ebd80b617d5b32a87","tid":1708255,"uid":33775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:56:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_706910_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_706910_0&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=fc16a9be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_706910_0&h=3f7bc158\" target=\"_blank\">https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_706910_0</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0Ghu1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0Ghu1E.jpg&h=9377edac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【1111三罷｜沙田】喬裝警新城市拘五示威者 速龍唔認得自己友打爆缸<br />\n5小時前    <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一批參加黎明行動的示威者，早上約七時十五分，進入港鐵沙田站時，突然有一批速龍小隊撲出，與現場多名喬裝警員合力制服示威者。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名戴口罩的學生打扮的示威者，懷疑太入型入格，被速龍誤以為是真示威者，揮棍毆爆缸，該喬裝警馬上表明自己人，並立即撲前壓住示威者以證明身份，事件中有四男一女被捕。<br />\n<br />\n速龍小隊離開港鐵站時，有市民追住指罵，警員並以胡椒噴劑噴向市民和記者。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：陳三<br />\n<br />\n攝錄：阿晨"},{"pid":"d6fc7a3383e3c889d3d1fc58bec5ea7d8b27d306","tid":1708255,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecffdfc805f8f1361d7a3e356a21e77970d5887","tid":1708255,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"945865414e6689d21fa83a5d7a4451efec95b59d","tid":1708255,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy